OL,3,CWheelchair athlete powers through
OL,4,Chalfway mark in world record attempt
OL,6,FAn Exeter wheelchair athlete has made
OL,7,Fit to the halfway mark in her bid to
OL,8,Fset a world record.
OL,10,FLexi Chambers had her leg amputated
OL,11,Fthree years ago and experiences three
OL,12,Fchronic pain conditions, leading to
OL,13,Fover 20 surgeries
OL,15,FShe was determined it wouldn't end her
OL,16,Fchances of taking part in sports and
OL,17,Fis now attempting to wheel 870 miles
OL,18,Ffrom John O'Groats to Lands End.
