OL,3,CWheelchair athlete powers through
OL,4,Chalfway mark in world record attempt
OL,6,FLexi is attempting to complete the
OL,7,Fchallenge in 35 days, which means
OL,8,Fshe's covering a marathon every day.
OL,10,FFor the past three years, Lexi has
OL,11,Fdedicated herself to endurance events
OL,12,F- raising vital funds for local
OL,13,Fcharities.
OL,15,FThis year she's supporting the Aaron
OL,16,FLewis Foundation and The Exeter Chiefs
OL,17,FFoundation - with the aim of providing
OL,18,Faccess to sport and wellbeing for all.
