OL,3,CWheelchair athlete powers through
OL,4,Chalfway mark in world record attempt
OL,6,FA fervent admirer of rugby and
OL,7,Finspired by the determination embedded
OL,8,Fin the women's game, Lexi will visit
OL,9,Frugby clubs along her journey.
OL,11,FThe Rugby Relay, passing on a signed
OL,12,Frugby ball from club to club, will
OL,13,Fconnect grassroots and professional
OL,14,Fclubs nationwide.
OL,16,FThis symbolises the inclusivity
OL,17,Fingrained within the rugby family and
OL,18,Femphasises the importance of unity and
OL,19,Fsupport.
