OL,3,CWheelchair athlete powers through
OL,4,Chalfway mark in world record attempt
OL,6,FShe set off from John O'Groats on 27
OL,7,FAugust, hopes to achieve her fifth
OL,8,Fworld record when she arrives at
OL,9,FLand's End on 10 October. At the
OL,10,Fweekend she passed through the north
OL,11,Fwest.
OL,13,FSpeaking on Monday 23 September, at
OL,14,Fthe end of the 28th day, she said:
OL,15,F"Everyday is rolling into one, to be
OL,16,Fhonest. What a day it was today - it
OL,17,Fwas really tough. Completely soaked
OL,18,Ffrom head to toe, everything was
OL,19,Fdrenched.
