OL,6,F"The hills just went on and on, it was
OL,7,Freally tough."
OL,9,FLexi said she's seen a really positive
OL,10,Fresponse from passers-by, including
OL,11,Fpeople getting out of their cars and
OL,12,Fclapping, and donations flooding in.
OL,14,F"Another day tomorrow, and fingers
OL,15,Fcrossed for no rain!"
OL,17,FThis gives you an idea of what Lexi's
OL,18,Fjourney looks like (footage from Lexi
OL,19,FChambers and PPA Sports Content)
