OL,3,CWheelchair athlete powers through
OL,4,Chalfway mark in world record attempt
OL,6,FSpeaking before the challenge, Lexi
OL,7,Fsaid: "I had to change my expectations
OL,8,Fand dreams, and adapt and overcome
OL,9,Fperceived barriers to sport.
OL,11,F"Since then I have dedicated my time
OL,12,Fto completing endurance events to
OL,13,Fassist with charity fundraising, and
OL,14,Fraise awareness of the fact that you
OL,15,Fcan achieve what you can with what you
OL,16,Fhave.
OL,18,F"I didn't have access to a sports
OL,19,Fwheelchair, and in this economic
OL,20,Fclimate, not many people do.
OL,26,@oD@GOUzD@AOU
