OL,3,CWheelchair athlete powers through
OL,4,Chalfway mark in world record attempt
OL,6,F"So I want to show people that you
OL,7,Fdon't need one to engage in sport. You
OL,8,Fcan still be fit and active using the
OL,9,Fkit which you do have access to.
OL,11,F"My goal is to inspire by
OL,12,Fdemonstrating that despite adversity,
OL,13,Fachieving dreams is possible."
OL,15,FShe has already broken world records
OL,16,Ffor the fastest half and full
OL,17,Fmarathons using a non-sport wheelchair.
