OL,3,CWheelchair athlete powers through
OL,4,Chalfway mark in world record attempt
OL,6,FIn August 2023 Lexi wheeled non-stop
OL,7,Faround an athletics track for 12
OL,8,Fhours, again gaining her 4th world
OL,9,Frecord and raising more money for
OL,10,Fcharity.
OL,12,FIf she completes her journey to Lands
OL,13,FEnd, that would be her 5th world
OL,14,Frecord.
OL,16,FShe is due to reach the West Country
OL,17,Fclubs at the end of September.
